<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>404 â€” Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
      min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 2rem;
    }
    .code { font-size: 8rem; font-weight: 900; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #60a5fa); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin: .5rem 0 1rem; color: #e2e8f0; }
    p { color: #94a3b8; }
    .url { display: inline-block; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15); border-radius: 6px; padding: .3rem .75rem; font-family: monospace; color: #fbbf24; margin: .75rem 0 1.5rem; }
    .actions { margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }
    a.btn { text-decoration: none; padding: .65rem 1.4rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn-primary  { background: #6366f1; color: #fff; }
    .btn-secondary { background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); color: #e2e8f0; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div>
    <div class="code">404</div>
    <h1>Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>We couldn't find the page you were looking for.</p>
    <div class="url"><%= url %></div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Go Home</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="javascript:history.back()">Go Back</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>